<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩ - في حديث <span class="c2">(٤٠٤)</span>: فيها: <span class="c1">"عمي"</span>،<span class="c5"> بدل:</span> <span class="c1">"عمر"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
